window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Meeting an old enemy will lead to a chain of unexpected discoveries, encounters, and a contract that you don't want, but you have to make, because evil never slumbers.</p> <p>High levels, ranks, and titles that the citizens of Drikar struggle to normally achieve are a tempting reward. Most importantly, they all belong to the same sect....</p> <p>It would be all right, because Raven has emerged victorious from bleaker fights before, but this time, the stakes are much, much higher.</p>"; 
